{"tid":2035660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一男子向提私人檢控郭榮鏗14項「公職人員行為失當」罪 　法庭審視證據後再作決定","createTime":"2020-05-26T05:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T06:52:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf29a340e8592e298f64bc137fa6601c40f0705","tid":2035660,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1528387_1_L_20200526123038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1528387_1_L_20200526123038.jpg&h=7d624cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名香港男商人，不滿早前主持立法會內會會議的議員郭榮鏗，拖延內會會議，在沙田裁判法院向郭榮鏗提出私人檢控，控告他14項「公職人員行為失當」罪。法庭將審視相關證據後，決定是否受理。<br />\n<br />\n入稟人是一名從事貿易及出入口的男商人，無政治背景，由早前負責時任立法會議員區諾軒「大聲公襲警」案件的大律師陳文慧、律師陳永良代表，法律團隊亦包括前任裁判官、現任大律師黃汝榮。檢控文件包括當事人供辭、公開會議紀錄及片段等，不排除會傳召熟悉議事規則的證人作供。<br />\n<br />\n男商人表示，由去年10月至今年4月，透過公開片段看到郭榮鏗主持內會，其間14次處理不相干的事宜、拖延選舉主席，令大部分法案不能提交大會表決及通過，影響民生，認為郭榮鏗太過份，自己看不過眼，決定提告。"},{"pid":"6343d113e496514c78512bd3c629ba02d0625707","tid":2035660,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"留名等睇唔受理/DoJ強行接管<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f262a00e132ba455e08c545eb2448754b984b56","tid":2035660,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"法庭唔會介立立法會事務，完"},{"pid":"ab6293e95b63568682e2be7fc3c2ea8882e91d36","tid":2035660,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f262a00e132ba455e08c545eb2448754b984b56","tid":2035660,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"法庭唔會介立立法會事務，完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:32:52.000Z","msg":"今時今日你咁肯定？"},{"pid":"9567102cdb4f955963957af85ccb33d93bf3e9ec","tid":2035660,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f262a00e132ba455e08c545eb2448754b984b56","tid":2035660,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"法庭唔會介立立法會事務，完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"唔會主動介入但有人放上枱就第二樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5340c10c50622732dc13d7e6897e53a31b7b514","tid":2035660,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6343d113e496514c78512bd3c629ba02d0625707","tid":2035660,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"留名等睇唔受理/DoJ強行接管<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"唔會成功啦<br />\n律政司先會告得入"},{"pid":"2881fd0777cd990667547db19cf28963262f406c","tid":2035660,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"如果告到<br />\n律政司一早告左<br />\n點會搞到要搵大口狗洗橫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdf4ae6ddffdd80edd978a7792f00a6500f6783","tid":2035660,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:20:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfc319a88b690c230687a21c4d8e8a56bb82ac07","tid":2035660,"uid":69544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"想知條友乜水"},{"pid":"41be0da4c17fba05239de0c9e9a5f3c4122cd134","tid":2035660,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"$$$<br />\nSigh..."}]}